Author: mymincome
Title: [ANN] [ICO & BOUNTY] ðŸ’°ðŸ”¥myMincomeðŸ”¥ðŸ’° Basic Income, Index Fund, Payment Solution ðŸš€ðŸš€
Body: We have added our FAQ on the first page.  FAQ  How do you operate to earn money? We charge a management fee of 1,5% p.a for investing in our Index Fund. We take a 5% commission on every raffle ticket we sold and a 2% fee on our lending program. Furthermore we do arbitrage trading with the biggest exchanges in Hong Kong, Japan and Afrika. This is our biggest potential.  How can I earn money? We enable you to share in the company's success. Every coin holder will receive interest up to 10% on monthly basis. You can take part in our lending program to earn more interest, invest in our Index Fund, or get a Basic Income. Besides, we will buy back our coins to increase the price.  Do you have a price projection for INC? We start selling INC in the presale for $ 0.05 up to $ 0.10 in the main sale. In May we start to buy our coins back to increase the value. It starts at $ 0.15. We expect a price increase of at least $ 0.25 until the External Exchange opens at the end of July.  How does the Global Basic Income work? We sell tickets for our regular raffle. The raffle will be broadcast on youtube. The winner receives an income of 1 ETH per month for one year. All those who participated in our ICO will automatically take part in the first raffles.  What currencies can I use to participate in the ICO? We accept ETH - please send it from you ERC-20 compatible wallet. We recommend MyEtherWallet or Metamask.  What are the benefits of an ICO? Early investors who believe in us can buy INC on a lower ICO price - $0.05-$0.10. Furthermore they get discount on our Index Fund and free raffle tickets.  How can I add the tokens to my wallet? You have to use a ERC-20 compatible wallet. We recommend myetherwallet or metamask. Click on "ADD TOKEN" and use the contract Address:  0x6a977f55dbc92b4798f6bd20e274d5b98aa2008c Token Symbol: INC and Decimals: 18.   Where can I buy the Index Fund? The Index Fund is designed on the 0x-blockchain. We will announce the launch on our website in early June.  If there are unsold coins, what will happen with them? Unsold coins will be burned after the main sale to keep the value high.  What will I earn if I participate in the bounty program ICO? We have reserved 5,000,000 tokens for our bounty program. Please visit our Bitcointalk page for all information.  IÂ´m an USA resident. Can I buy myMincome token? Unfortunately we can not accept US residents, due to the regulations in the USA. We are sorry.  Can I trade my INC after the ICO? Yes, we plan to be listed on the first External Exchange in July 2018. In April we will open our Internal Exchange.  My question is not answered here! If you have other question, do not hesitate to contact us at support at mymincome.com.

Body: WEBSITE | FACEBOOK | TWITTER | TELEGRAM | MEDIUM    INC is a digital cryptocurrency with the aim to provide the easiest payment solution for online shopping and social media. We will make it easier to invest in cryptocurrencies. Furthermore we will distribute a global Basic Income on the Blockchain.   ICO Pre-sale: 9th March 2018 14:00 UTC â€“ 1 INC = 0.05 USD ICO Main Flash Sale: March 17th, 2018 14:00 UTC â€“ 1 INC = 0.08 USD ICO Main Sale: March 25th, 2018 14:00 UTC â€“ 1 INC = 0.10 USD           INC PAYMENT. Social Messenger Integration and Browser Payment Plugin. There is no easier way to send coins to other users and to pay in online shops.  Social Messenger Integration. We are working on a Social Messenger Integration for all big Messengers like facebook, twitter, WhatsApp, Telegram, and YouTube. Users can send INC coins to familymembers, friends or other users, as well as receive payments for money collectings like crowdfundings etc. just by using your favorite Messenger App.  Browser Plugin. We have created a browser plugin for firefox and google chrome, which allows you to pay with cryptocurrencies in every partner online shop. The plugin works as a proxy between the online shop and your INC-coins. As soon as you make a purchase, your coins will instantaneously be exchanged in any currency requested by the shop.    INDEX FUND INVESTMENT. Invest in our Index Fund, it contains the top 10 cryptocurrencies like for example Bitcoin, Eather, Ripple, Litecoin, Neo, Iota and more, weighted by market capitalization and rebalances monthly. This strategy is associated with lower risks and at the same time with higher profits. The Index Fund strategy is backtested since January 2017 and has shown remarkable results with lower risk than only investing  in bitcoin. The following Chat represent the profit by investing only 100 $ in the Fund INDEX Top10 from january to december 2017.     P2P MARKETPLACE. Our Shareholders are given a share of the profits. Anyone who is holding INC will automatically participate in our airdrops. You will receive interest up to 10% on monthly basis payed in INC. Commission payouts are secured by smart contracts and  provide token holders an almost endless source of income. We will be buying INC back in order to provide the supply for our regularly airdrops, which will also increase the price. The first repurchase starts in May for 0.20 USD/INC.    P2P RAFFLE. We will organize regular raffles, where you can win a Basic Income with monthly payments for one year. The payments will be executed in the value of 1 ETH per month. You have the opportunity in participate in our regular raffles by buying our limited raffle tickets. All our token holder who participate in our ICO will automatically take part in our first raffle.       Symbol: INC Type: ERC-20 Decimals: 18 Contract: 0x6a977f55dbc92b4798f6bd20e274d5b98aa2008c  ICO Supply: 60.000.000 Total Supply: 100.000.000 Softcap: 15.000.000  ICO: 60% Staking: 20% Reserve: 15% Bounty: 5%  Monthly Airdrops: 10%       PRE-ICO BOUNTY PROGRAM.   The myMincome platform will be distributed using a Pre-ICO Bounty program to ensure a high market penetration. Users of the myMincome Platform can earn INC tokens participating on our bounty program:  - Bitcointalk Signatures. Participants of the Bitcointalk forum, can spread the ICO release on a signature. The reward depends on the ranking of the participants and is determined on the number of stakes they get.  - Writing Articles. We offer tokens to bloggers for writing featured articles about our ICO on their blogs. The reward depends on the number of followers and readers and on the engagement level of the articles and blog posts.  - Translation work: This involves translating all documents pertaining to the myMincome Platform as well as moderating different forum groups (Website, Whitepaper, the Bitcointalk ANN thread, etc.). We offer INC tokens for all native speakers of the languages Japanese, French, Spanish, Dutch, German, Chinese and othes.  - You can earn INC Tokens by producing videos on YouTube, this includes to create a video about myMincome and to share it with your followers. What currencies can I use to participate in the ICO? We accept ETH - please send it from you ERC-20 compatible wallet. We recommend MyEtherWallet or Metamask.  What are the benefits of an ICO? Early investors who believe in us can buy INC on a lower ICO price - $0.05-$0.10. Furthermore they get discount on our Index Fund and free raffle tickets.  How can I add the tokens to my wallet? You have to use a ERC-20 compatible wallet. We recommend myetherwallet or metamask. Click on "ADD TOKEN" and use the contract Address: 0x6a977f55dbc92b4798f6bd20e274d5b98aa2008c Token Symbol: INC and Decimals: 18.    Where can I buy the Index Fund? The Index Fund is designed on the 0x-blockchain. We will announce the launch on our website in early June.  If there are unsold coins, what will happen with them? Unsold coins will be burned after the main sale to keep the value high.  What will I earn if I participate in the bounty program ICO? We have reserved 5,000,000 tokens for our bounty program. Please visit our Bitcointalk page for all information.  IÂ´m an USA resident. Can I buy myMincome token? Unfortunately we can not accept US residents, due to the regulations in the USA. We are sorry.  Can I trade my INC after the ICO? Yes, we plan to be listed on the first External Exchange in July 2018. In April we will open our Internal Exchange.  My question is not answered here! If you have other question, do not hesitate to contact us at support at mymincome.com.       WEBSITE | FACEBOOK | TWITTER | TELEGRAM | MEDIUM
